<div class="about-main">
  <div id="opening-statement">
    <p>
      DeCareer Builders Academy (DCBA) was founded with the goal of addressing
      the growing skills gap in the job market. Recognizing the need for a
      platform that not only provides theoretical knowledge but also hands-on
      experience, DCBA was launched to offer tailored courses, career coaching,
      and our flagship WorkXperience program. Over the years, we have helped
      countless individuals gain valuable industry insights, work experience,
      and personalized career guidance, positioning them for success in their
      chosen paths.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="ms-vs">
    <div id="ms">
      <h4>Mission Statement</h4>
      <p>
        At DeCareer Builders Academy (DCBA), our mission is to empower
        individuals to unlock their career potential by offering comprehensive
        career development solutions, hands-on work experience, and personalized
        coaching. Through innovative courses, practical skills training, and a
        supportive learning environment, we aim to bridge the gap between
        education and employment, helping individuals excel in their chosen
        fields.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div id="vs">
      <h4>Vision Statement</h4>
      <p>
        Our vision is to be a global leader in career development, offering
        transformative learning experiences that equip individuals with the
        skills, confidence, and real-world expertise they need to thrive in
        today’s competitive job market. We envision a future where every learner
        has access to personalized guidance, meaningful work experience, and
        industry-relevant knowledge to achieve their professional dreams.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
